{"tid":2373369,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場： 候任政助張進樂入政府後一個月才辭顧問公司董事 疑與其公職有利益衝突","createTime":"2021-01-20T11:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T13:29:57.000Z","uid":22556,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e650dbbd4ffbc79942f37d3858d5c8c985d01c3c","tid":2373369,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:44:11.000Z","msg":"民政事務局政治助理一職，有傳將由局長徐英偉心腹、該局研究主任張進樂接任，張有望成為最年輕的政助，月薪並由現時 6.7 萬元躍升至約 10 萬元。不過《立場》調查發現，去年 11 月加入政府的張進樂，一直是其創立私人公司「易顧問」的董事及唯一股東，直至 12 月底才辭任，由於未有文件顯示他轉讓股份，他目前或仍持股。據悉，「易顧問」曾承接大學外判工作，而張一直從事政策研究，其公司或與其公職有衝突。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%82%B3%E6%8E%A5%E4%BB%BB%E5%BE%90%E8%8B%B1%E5%81%89%E6%94%BF%E5%8A%A9-%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%BB%E5%BC%B5%E9%80%B2%E6%A8%82%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%80%BE%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E5%A7%8B%E8%BE%AD%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B-%E6%8B%92%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E6%9C%89%E5%90%A6%E7%94%B3%E5%A0%B1/?fbclid=IwAR2hRBVG6Z1hmQgEtE34j2IvmleMl8zE4xem47Yk3fu1VkzY2XVE69HyXp0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%258E%25A5%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%25BE%2590%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%2581%2589%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258A%25A9-%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E9%2580%25B2%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E9%2580%25BE%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588-%25E5%25A7%258B%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E5%2595%258F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E8%2591%25A3%25E4%25BA%258B-%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2590%25A6%25E7%2594%25B3%25E5%25A0%25B1%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2hRBVG6Z1hmQgEtE34j2IvmleMl8zE4xem47Yk3fu1VkzY2XVE69HyXp0&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia7y9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=e63d353a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%258E%25A5